BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:_rae49Xm5j_9TO8PwGtRW
SUMMARY:Swinson &amp\; The Expedition @ Perihelion Brewery
DTSTAMP:20260413T010440Z
DTSTART:20260513T020000Z
DESCRIPTION:Drawing on their love of Pacific Northwest History and blending
	 their disparate indie rock influences (Eric worships Howe Gelb and Janet 
	Weiss\, while Sam adores Lonely Forest and Keith Moon)\, Swinson and the E
	xpedition is historic concept rock that has the looseness of a 1960s count
	ry house band\, an element of basement psychedelia\, and the intensity and
	 rage of the Vikings from which Eric traces his ancestry.\n\nhttps://www.p
	erihelion.beer/events/2026/4/12/swinson-amp-the-expedition-perihelion-brew
	ery
URL:https://www.perihelion.beer/events/2026/4/12/swinson-amp-the-expedition
	-perihelion-brewery
LOCATION:Perihelion Brewery\, 2800 16th Ave South\, Seattle\, WA 98144
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
