BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:6OivXs1kZeCFVEHWXFGkH
SUMMARY:John Pronto @ Perihelion Brewery
DTSTAMP:20260413T010440Z
DTSTART:20260708T020000Z
DESCRIPTION:John Pronto blends the soul of folk\, the grit of blues\, and t
	he openness of Americana into a sound that feels both timeless and deeply 
	personal. His music captures the essence of life’s struggles and triumphs\
	, exploring love\, heartache\, and redemption with unfiltered honesty. Wit
	h a voice that carries both warmth and raw emotion\, Pronto draws from the
	 storytelling traditions of American roots music. Join us for this perform
	ance in the outdoor patio space!\n\nhttps://www.perihelion.beer/events/202
	6/4/12/john-pronto-perihelion-brewery
URL:https://www.perihelion.beer/events/2026/4/12/john-pronto-perihelion-bre
	wery
LOCATION:Perihelion Brewery\, 2800 16th Ave South\, Seattle\, WA 98144
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:HWRk3p_7dFAHqAYp-K8ch
SUMMARY: Chase Rabideau @ Perihelion Brewery 
DTSTAMP:20260413T010440Z
DTSTART:20260715T020000Z
DESCRIPTION:A professional guitarist and singer of many musical backgrounds
	\, Chase Rabideau is a crowd-centered entertainer with a background in man
	y popular genres. Along with folk/rock centric original music that can be 
	found online\, Chase plays over 400 covers in a variety of genres such as 
	rock ‘n roll (50’s\, 60’s\, 70’s\, +more)\, classic country\, folk\, R&B\,
	 jazz\, blues\, folk/pub songs from Ireland\, (seasonal) Christmas music\,
	 and crowd-favorite popular music.\n\nhttps://www.perihelion.beer/events/2
	026/2/24/chase-rabideau-perihelion-brewery-mpbj4
URL:https://www.perihelion.beer/events/2026/2/24/chase-rabideau-perihelion-
	brewery-mpbj4
